Package: freedom
Title: Demonstration of Disease Freedom (DDF)
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Rosendal", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "trosendal@gmail.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6576-9668"))
Description: Implements the formulae required to calculate freedom
    from disease according to Cameron and Baldock (1998)
    <doi:10.1016/S0167-5877(97)00081-0>. These are the
    methods used at the Swedish national veterinary institute (SVA) to
    evaluate the performance of our nation animal disease
    surveillance programmes.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/SVA-SE/freedom
BugReports: https://github.com/SVA-SE/freedom/issues
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
